Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:12.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就沒有什麼能把高木同學嚇得尖叫的辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:19.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之 像這樣每天都被她捉弄的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:21.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:28.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:30.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:33.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:35.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:41.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起去學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:19.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比身高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:23.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:26.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剛才被她看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:29.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:32.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要一起騎車去學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:34.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:36.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被發現的話會挨罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:38.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是不好意思才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:40.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:41.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:47.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看來我撞上電線杆的事情沒被她看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:53.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片也終於換長袖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:58.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最近變冷了 感覺差不多該換了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你長個了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:08.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,春天的時候感覺你的制服比現在寬鬆一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:10.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:16.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在有種「制服 is 正義」的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:20.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道我到發育期了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:27.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 最近一個勁地長個子 真難辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道到了發育期嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:33.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學倒是沒感覺有什麼變化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你這可是性騷擾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,居然說沒變化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:50.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不是這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說的是身高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在說身高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你以為我在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺你還是沒怎麼長高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不不 長高了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:21.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說不定我現在比高木同學還要高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那來比比身高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要來這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,穿著鞋子比不出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,小心遲到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來 背對背站好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:58.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺好暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:09.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一般不都是輪流貼著牆壁作記號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,兩個人背對著量更準嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,應該差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:20.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:24.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來嘛 西片也來確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我沒說錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:37.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你沒墊腳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 你居然懷疑我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:50.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,面對面的話 就算墊腳也會知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:55.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個 那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:07.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺好像我要高一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為我剛才墊腳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:13.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然墊腳了啊 大騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可沒有說過我沒墊腳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:19.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 終於贏過我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個高木同學 一副從容的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心裡肯定很不甘心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:31.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有 我沒有不甘心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:35.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為要是塊頭變大的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就會撞上電線杆 很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看到了嗎 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,走吧 去學校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 高木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有那麼冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:15.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉很怕冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:16.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 你手好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怕冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再這樣干我可饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們的手為什麼那麼冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手冷的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,內心很溫暖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:56.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得內心很溫暖的人不會做剛才那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:59.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了好了 別那麼記仇嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你再幹的話我真的要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:06.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你明明已經生氣了好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:12.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 不要啊早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是心暖攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,救命啊 由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是剛才的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:29.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉的手 好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但她的心拔涼拔涼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:37.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷啊 不要靠過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,心寒攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:40.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,走為上策
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:41.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你也可以摸回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:58.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好冷啊好冷啊 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:06.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能會這樣幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都叫你住手了 好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手冷的人 內心是暖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪裡暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木和西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天一起上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,關係真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他們果然在交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:43.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片和高木在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他們關係特別好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉 你很羨慕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 因為嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,與其說是羨慕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:01.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 由加莉說想和男生唧唧我我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才沒這樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈 你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要突然跟我搭話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,本來快要尿出來的 現在尿不出來了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:18.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個很有趣的 去看看比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 我會看的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:23.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:31.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想到了很厲害的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,如果是這個犀利的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放學的時候肯定能捉弄到高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在偷笑什麼呢 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:47.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好猥瑣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我才沒有想那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那種事情是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:54.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你臉好紅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我走著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:12.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 難道她發覺我在設計她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你要再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:22.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:27.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放學時你說不定還會改變主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以的話到時候再給我答覆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她究竟怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了 反正不被發覺就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天來我家玩超級大亂鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an7}原文スパプラ，應該是山寨明星大亂?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:53.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 又要陪女朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:57.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:59.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是高木同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哈？你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,根本就不是那回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木和西片沒在交往哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我剛才在廁所聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:11.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,突然想去小便了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,廁所…廁所…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那傢伙剛才在廁所幹什麼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然你們沒在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:30.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那為什麼你會和高木同學一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛 因為被她邀請了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這不就是因為在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:36.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,應該不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:44.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下節課要去實驗室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好 趕緊走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:13:01.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 我覺得高木同學只是想捉弄我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:05.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:08.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天不可以繞遠路了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:13.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我想吃椪柑冰棍 我想吃椪柑冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大冷天的還吃什麼冰棍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在被爐吃冰棍超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「給我答覆」也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:27.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要我重新邀請她的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺有點不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:35.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我還沒邀請過她一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:36.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:42.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 高木同學來問我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只要說個Yes就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:49.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天有人問我是不是在和西片交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:55.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後 我好像被認為是喜歡西片的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:14:00.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是不是因為總是我在邀請你一起回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來這就是你的目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:09.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,創造出讓我來邀請你的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:13.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後取笑我害羞的反應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:15.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要強裝平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「哼 這樣啊」這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:25.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:26.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:30.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 關於早上的答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:38.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正我沒什麼事 一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:42.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,加油啊我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要跨過了這一關
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:50.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我就能捉弄到高木同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:57.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一起回家怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:09.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:18.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片好像還有什麼計劃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然暴露了 那還是不要做比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:33.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但我好不容易想出來的點子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:37.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說我還完全沒想過要怎樣弄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要不要買果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:48.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺喉嚨乾乾的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大部分都賣完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明想喝冷飲的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:58.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,剩下的只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,紅豆湯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有獵奇的飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:03.23,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\pos(918,330)\frz3.238}艾草汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:03.23,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs50\pos(1164,702)}西瓜味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:08.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺無論選哪個都會後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,無論選哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要去別的自動販賣機看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:20.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我喉嚨也渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,總之先…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好難喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看包裝就能猜到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,錢白花了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣一來就能開始我的計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:44.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:51.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好喝的熱飲和難喝得要命的飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:02.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二選一問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:08.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好喝但是燙手的飲料和難喝得要命的飲料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難以選擇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:13.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你就犯難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:16.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓我看看你為難的表情 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:23.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是我喝了好喝的熱飲發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:25.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片會來探望我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:30.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這有什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:31.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,關係大著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:42.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我應該會去探望你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我選好喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學完全沒有為難嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:02.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不如說為難的是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,二選一問題的作戰失敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:09.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不 放棄還為之過早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:10.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那下一題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:16.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你是選一輩子沒有零花錢呢 還是不再捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一輩子沒有零花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:18.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:24.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為我有壓歲錢作積蓄 暫時沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:26.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到了高中只要打工就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:30.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所以還是選捉弄西片比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我太小瞧高木同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得問些更刁鑽的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:36.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,從剛才開始你就在問些奇怪的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說 你想讓我為難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:49.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒 沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:52.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我也要提問了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:58.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不在和被我捉弄一輩子 哪個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不在是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然我也不想被她捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:12.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但消失什麼的…那也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:15.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那 我選被你捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然喜歡被捉弄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:23.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有 肯定是討厭被捉弄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:28.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不太希望你消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說 你想一輩子和我在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你臉好紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讓我發窘就這麼有意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也得問個好問題才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼下一題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 還要繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:53.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一輩子考零分 以及和我接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:54.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:57.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接…接…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哪個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,考零分 看了書也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 無論幹什麼都是零分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:14.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣的話不僅以後肯定拿不到零花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,甚至連高中也上不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:20.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但要選了接吻的話 肯定會被她捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你很糾結嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:23.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我越糾結 高木同學她就越開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得趕緊作出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:31.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,零分太殘酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:32.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那 那就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,選不是考零分那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:41.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是考零分的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:47.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,接 接吻的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:10.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:14.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片的個子要高一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:17.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了西片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在比身高而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到頭來又被狠狠地捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我學到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:43.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,其中一個選項一定要是選不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:46.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只要另一個是捉弄用的選項
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:48.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這場對決就能穩贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 下一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:51.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼下一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:56.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,倒立著繞校園走一圈和兩個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:59.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,稍微等一下 我不會倒立
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:02.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說還輪不到我提問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:04.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,首先要回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:05.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 你看…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:50.07,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:54.49,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:01:04.79,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:13.63,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}校庭で君のことを一番に見つけて今日は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:21.89,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて話しかけようか？ ちょっと考えるの楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.85,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風に揺らされるカーテン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:30.23,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不意打ちに当たる日差し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:34.15,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}眩しそうな顔を笑ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:38.03,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}照れて伏せちゃうのね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:46.16,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}憂鬱なテストも吹き飛ばせるような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:54.42,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ねえ、二人で秘密の約束をしたいなって提案です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:59.84,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}勘違いされちゃったっていいよ、君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:03.85,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}なんて思ってたって言わないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:14.11,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}近づく空の香りを隣で感じていたいの
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:50.07,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:54.49,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:01:04.79,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:13.63,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在校園的庭院 第一個發現你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.67,0:01:21.89,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}今天要和你說些什麼呢 即便是想著這些也是一種樂趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.85,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}窗簾隨風起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:30.23,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不經意地投入一束陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:34.15,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那美麗的容顏笑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:38.03,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}羞得我抬不起頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:46.16,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}風兒喧囂 似要吹散考試的憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:54.42,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 我想要和你一起 立下兩人的秘密約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:59.84,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}會錯意了也沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:03.85,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}和你一起就是幸福 這樣想著卻不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:14.11,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}瀰漫在周圍的那陣幽香 想在你的身邊靜靜感受
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDJP——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:15.69,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}広い宇宙の数ある一つ　青い地球の広い世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:24.65,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}小さな恋の思いは届く　小さな島のあなたのもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:30.70,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}あなたと出会い　時は流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:35.37,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}思いをこめた　手紙もふえる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:40.29,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}いつしか二人互いに響く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:45.01,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}時に激しく　時に切なく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:49.68,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響くは遠く　遥か彼方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.43,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}優しい歌は　世界を変える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:01.23,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　あなたにとって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:07.24,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}大事な人ほど　すぐそばにいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:13.37,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ただあなたにだけ　届いて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:16.75,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}響け恋の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:25.71,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:34.76,Takagisan-OPEDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}ほら　響け恋の歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——EDCH——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:15.69,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}想把這遼闊宇宙中絕無僅有的小小的相思之情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:24.65,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}傳達給蔚藍地球上廣闊世界中小小島嶼上的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:30.70,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}與你邂逅 光陰飛逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:35.37,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}飽含思念的信件堆積如山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:40.29,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不知不覺我們心生共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:45.01,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}時而充滿激情 時而傷感不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:49.68,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}迴響漸漸遠去 到那遙遠彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.43,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你那溫柔的歌聲 改變了我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:01.23,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你看 對你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:07.24,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}重要的人近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:13.37,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}只願你能感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:16.75,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}這響徹天地的戀歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:25.71,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}你聽 你聽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:31.05,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}聽見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:34.76,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}這響徹天地的戀歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——STAFF——
